SIMPLE: almighty
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Almighty
<hw>Al*might"y</hw> <pr>(⟦add⟧l*m⟦imac⟧t"⟦ycr⟧)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[AS. <ets>ealmihtig</ets>, <ets>⟦ae⟧lmihtig</ets>; <ets>eal</ets>
(OE. <ets>al</ets>) all + <ets>mihtig</ets> mighty.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Unlimited in might; omnipotent; all-powerful;
irresistible.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>I am the <qex>Almighty</qex> God.</q> <rj><qau>Gen. xvii.
1.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Great; extreme; terrible.</def>
<mark>[Slang]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Poor Aroar can not live, and can not die, -- so that he is in an
<qex>almighty</qex> fix.</q> <rj><qau>De Quincey.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>The Almighty</b></col>, <cd>the omnipotent God.</cd>
<rj><au>Rev. i. 8.</au></rj></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Almner</ent>⟦br⟧
